{"tid":1295390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你知條撚呀 打篇水蛇春長文屌人唔走好柒","createTime":"2019-07-08T04:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T07:10:19.000Z","uid":249040,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"574a737cb78e0547d226f36d713f02abda9a1aae","tid":1295390,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"人又唔係現場，又跟唔足全程直播，仲係度懶醒個啲撚樣呀<br />\n<br />\n至少我聽到蘋果直播，訪問旺角其中一個人話 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔係唔肯走， 係收到tg話宜家走 會被狗係不同街口包抄 單打獨鬥係暗角無人睇到 不如係有鏡頭情況下再睇情況諗計走 明唔明？ </span></span><br />\n<br />\n係度嘈嘈閉，你估去到旺角d人真係唔想撤呀<br />\n<br />\n就算唔想撤，又點， 點樣決定同判斷真係唔洗你教，係現場嘅人有自己原因。由六月頭開始大家本來就無客觀勝算，咪又走到宜家<br />\n咁有氣力打咁長篇野， 呢個時候點解唔用黎追討啲狗！"},{"pid":"e5f841b39320a12fabebb5a37f5ea58668e99218","tid":1295390,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a3216ad2cbc4e6e448e72ce7ecf6d3082ecf3c3","tid":1295390,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fb68c7e841933606573c620cb156f002764b274","tid":1295390,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b13684a31c914debda2354b30545135121804cc","tid":1295390,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f14358cd0828564c5b06b2f959eeec4c269b00a","tid":1295390,"uid":9103,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫人留，我都支持散<br />\n<br />\n但見仲有人係現場/人地唔散就鬧，又話人唔夠醒<br />\n<br />\n一副網路軍師樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警亂推，叫散但包抄唔先屌，先屌自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue